{"tid":1519460,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國要求中國償還清朝發行債券","createTime":"2019-08-30T14:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T16:52:29.000Z","uid":66271,"like":79,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"a6b117ec367ca4fc0ab0d125de11db61a0b6da69","tid":1519460,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:46:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">美國政府正在商討要求中國政府償還1912年前清政府所發行債券一事。<br />\n<br />\n彭博社週四（8月29日）發佈消息稱，美國數千居民持有清政府發行的過期債券。</span><br />\n<br />\n據Gazeta.ru網站報道，中華人民共和國成立後，新政府拒絕償還這些債券。<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普以及財政部長和商務部長接見了一些債券持有人。<br />\n<br />\n其間， 債券持有人提出可以把這些債券作為中美貿易爭端中的一個籌碼。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據美國債券持有人基金一位創始人的計算，考慮到通貨膨脹、利息和賠償費用，中國應支付超過1萬億美元。</span>"},{"pid":"36b1eed23faf6b07c0dc73e05aa101b4cb04d951","tid":1519460,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0vTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=26e642b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0vTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=4fe6171e